       fhir:definition [ fhir:v "An absolute URI that is used to identify this plan definition when it is referenced in a specification, model, design or an instance. This SHALL be a URL, SHOULD be globally unique, and SHOULD be an address at which this plan definition is (or will be) published. The URL SHOULD include the major version of the plan definition. For more information see [Technical and Business Versions](http://hl7.org/fhir/STU3/resource.html#versions)." ] ;
